2013年8月，[[派拉蒙影业|派拉蒙影业]]宣布[[克里斯托弗·麦奎里|克里斯托弗·麦奎里]]将执导第五部《碟中谍》电影，德鲁·皮尔斯将担纲编剧，[[汤姆·克鲁斯|汤姆·克鲁斯]]继续出演[[伊森·亨特|伊森·亨特]]。汤姆·克鲁斯制片团队和[[坏机器人制片公司|坏机器人制片公司]]将担任制片方，天空之舞制片公司将担任最后一部作品的联合投资方和执行制片方，在开发和制作过程中与团队紧密合作<ref name=paramountPR2013>{{cite press release | url= http://www.paramount.com/news-and-social-media/news-and-press-releases/paramount-pictures-and-skydance-productions-tap | title= Paramount Pictures and Skydance Productions Tap Christopher McQuarrie to Direct the Next 'Mission: Impossible' | publisher= [[Paramount_Pictures|Paramount Pictures]] | date= 2013-08-05 | accessdate= 2015-06-22 | archivedate= 2013-08-21 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130821043951/http://www.paramount.com/news-and-social-media/news-and-press-releases/paramount-pictures-and-skydance-productions-tap | deadurl= yes }}</ref>。2013年11月14日，派拉蒙宣布影片定档2015年12月25日<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/111364-mission-impossible-5-to-hit-theaters-december-25-2015 |title=Mission: Impossible 5 to Hit Theaters December 25, 2015 |last=Lesnick |first=Silas |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2013-11-14 |accessdate=2015-06-22 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ZTqVc3MN?url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/111364-mission-impossible-5-to-hit-theaters-december-25-2015 |archivedate=2015-06-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。同月，[[西蒙·佩吉|西蒙·佩吉]]证实将继续出演班吉一角<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1717570/simon-pegg-mission-impossible-5/|title=Simon Pegg Confirms He’s 'Absolutely' Returning For 'Mission: Impossible 5'|first=Kevin p.|last=Sullivan|date=2013-11-15|work=MTV News|accessdate=2015-06-22|archivedate=2014-08-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828195807/http://www.mtv.com/news/1717570/simon-pegg-mission-impossible-5/|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2014年5月，威尔·斯台普斯取代皮尔斯担任编剧<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hollywoodreporter.com/news/mission-impossible-5-will-staples-702708|title='Mission: Impossible 5' Taps New Writer (Exclusive)|last=Kit|first=Borys|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-05-09|accessdate=2014-05-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140511202014/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/mission-impossible-5-will-staples-702708|archivedate=2014-05-11|deadurl=no}}</ref>。同月，[[杰瑞米·雷纳|杰瑞米·雷纳]]证实他将继续出演威廉·勃兰特一角<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.yahoo.com/tv/bp/jeremy-renner-talks-narrating--the-world-wars---guest-starring-on--louie---and-flipping-homes-231619713.html | title=Jeremy Renner Talks Narrating 'The World Wars,' Guest Starring on 'Louie,' and Flipping Homes | publisher=Yahoo! | first=Kimberly | last=Potts | date=2014-05-21 | accessdate=2015-06-22 | archivedate=2015-03-26 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326010511/https://www.yahoo.com/tv/bp/jeremy-renner-talks-narrating--the-world-wars---guest-starring-on--louie---and-flipping-homes-231619713.html | deadurl=no }}</ref>，克鲁斯表示影片将在伦敦拍摄<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/active/10860514/Tom-Cruise-returns-to-London-to-film-Mission-Impossible-5.html | title=Tom Cruise returns to London to film 'Mission Impossible 5' | work=The Telegraph | location=UK | date=2014-05-29 | accessdate=2014-05-29 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006091335/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/active/10860514/Tom-Cruise-returns-to-London-to-film-Mission-Impossible-5.html | archivedate=2014-10-06 | deadurl=no }}</ref>，后来的报道表示影片将于8月在[[维也纳|维也纳]]开机<ref>{{cite news|last1=Daniels|first1=Nia|title=Mission: Impossible 5 takes Tom Cruise to Vienna|url=http://www.kftv.com/news/2014/07/08/Mission-Impossible-5-takes-Tom-Cruise-to-Vienna|accessdate=2014-07-14|publisher=KFTV.com (Wilmington Publishing & Information Ltd.)|location=UK|8=|date=2014-07-08|archivedate=2014-11-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141103230039/http://www.kftv.com/news/2014/07/08/Mission-Impossible-5-takes-Tom-Cruise-to-Vienna|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

2014年7月，[[蕾貝卡·弗格森_(演員)|蕾貝卡·弗格森]]加盟剧组，而[[亚历克·鲍德温|亚历克·鲍德温]]为第五部电影进行谈判<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=120362 |title=Mission: Impossible 5 Finds Its Female Lead in Rebecca Ferguson |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713034249/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=120362 |archive-date=2014-07-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=120359 |title=Mission: Impossible 5 Targets Alec Baldwin as CIA Head |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713034242/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=120359 |archive-date=2014-07-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。鲍德温于2014年8月证实加盟剧组<ref name="SetPhotos1">{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=122144 |title=First Photos from the Set of Mission: Impossible 5! |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2014-08-21 |accessdate=2014-08-21 |archivedate=2015-07-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714171415/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/122144-first-photos-from-the-set-of-mission-impossible-5 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，[[文·雷姆斯|文·雷姆斯]]证实将回归出演路德·斯迪克尔一角<ref>{{cite news|title=Ving Rhames Returns for Mission: Impossible 5|url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/312893-ving-rhames-returns-for-mission-impossible-5|accessdate=2014-08-17|publisher=www.superherohype.com|date=2014-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819090253/http://www.superherohype.com/news/312893-ving-rhames-returns-for-mission-impossible-5|archive-date=2014-08-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月5日，西恩·哈里斯正为反派角色进行谈判<ref>{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr|first1=Mike|title=Paramount Courts Sean Harris For ‘Mission: Impossible 5′ Villainy|url=http://deadline.com/2014/09/paramount-courts-sean-harris-for-mission-impossible-5-villainy-829763/|accessdate=2014-09-05|publisher=deadline.com|date=2014-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906064840/http://deadline.com/2014/09/paramount-courts-sean-harris-for-mission-impossible-5-villainy-829763/|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月2日，西蒙·麦克伯尼加入电影剧组<ref name=McBurney>{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title=Simon McBurney Joins Tom Cruise in ‘Mission: Impossible 5′|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/simon-mcburney-mission-impossible-5-1201288000/|accessdate=2014-10-03|publisher=variety.com|date=2014-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006162909/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/simon-mcburney-mission-impossible-5-1201288000/|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月6日，中国女演员[[张静初|张静初]]加盟参演<ref>{{cite web|title=张静初加盟《碟中谍5》 出演重要反派 对戏阿汤哥|url=http://news.mtime.com/2014/10/07/1532409.html|website=Mtime时光网|accessdate=2015-07-30|date=2014-10-07|language=zh-cn|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914232159/http://news.mtime.com/2014/10/07/1532409.html|archive-date=2015-09-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Jingchu>{{cite news|last1=Frater|first1=Patrick|title=Chinese Actress Zhang Jingchu Accepts ‘Mission’ With Tom Cruise|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/chinese-actress-zhang-jingchu-accepts-mission-with-tom-cruise-1201322089/|accessdate=2014-10-07|publisher=variety.com|date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008052859/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/chinese-actress-zhang-jingchu-accepts-mission-with-tom-cruise-1201322089/|archive-date=2014-10-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年3月22日，派拉蒙透露影片正式名称为《碟中谍5：神秘国度》，同期发行的还有前期海报和预告片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/mission-impossible-5-gets-a-783531|title='Mission: Impossible 5' Gets a 'Rogue' Name, Trumps 'Star Wars'|author=Pamela McClintock|work=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2015-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304042439/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/mission-impossible-5-gets-a-783531|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 摄制 ===
2014年8月，影片开机。8月21日，制片方发布[[奥地利|奥地利]][[维也纳|维也纳]]拍摄现场的第一组照片<ref name="SetPhotos1" />。8月22日，演员克鲁斯和佩吉与克里斯托弗·麦奎里现身[[维也纳地铁|维也纳地铁]]<ref name=express.co.uk>{{cite news|last1=Takyi|first1=Stephanie|title=Daredevil Tom Cruise hangs from the Vienna Opera House for Mission: Impossible 5 shoot|url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/showbiz/502543/Daredevil-Tom-Cruise-hangs-from-the-Vienna-Opera-House-for-Mission-Impossible-5-shoot|accessdate=2014-08-28|publisher=express.co.uk|date=2014-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140825230040/http://www.express.co.uk/news/showbiz/502543/Daredevil-Tom-Cruise-hangs-from-the-Vienna-Opera-House-for-Mission-Impossible-5-shoot|archive-date=2014-08-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。随后的日子里，克鲁斯和弗格森在[[维也纳国家歌剧院|维也纳国家歌剧院]]屋顶拍摄特技（跳跃）场景<ref name="express.co.uk" /><ref>{{cite news|last1=Holubiak|first1=Ian|title=Tom Cruise and Rebecca Ferguson Scale the Vienna Opera House for Their Latest 'Mission: Impossible 5'|url=http://www.classicalite.com/articles/10844/20140826/tom-cruise-and-rebecca-ferguson-scale-the-vienna-opera-house-for-their-latest-mission-impossible-5.htm|accessdate=2014-08-28|publisher=classicalite.com|date=2014-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828101410/http://www.classicalite.com/articles/10844/20140826/tom-cruise-and-rebecca-ferguson-scale-the-vienna-opera-house-for-their-latest-mission-impossible-5.htm|archive-date=2014-08-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。8月26日，演员们再度现身维也纳拍摄现场<ref>{{cite news|last=Betiku|first=Fehintola|title=Make 'em laugh... Tom Cruise exchanges jokes with Simon Pegg and Christopher McQuarrie on set of Mission: Impossible 5|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2736041/Tom-Cruise-exchanges-jokes-Simon-Pegg-Christopher-McQuarrie-set-Mission-Impossible-5.html|accessdate=2014-08-28|work=Daily Mail|location=UK|date=2014-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828002028/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2736041/Tom-Cruise-exchanges-jokes-Simon-Pegg-Christopher-McQuarrie-set-Mission-Impossible-5.html|archive-date=2014-08-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月30日，在奥地利历时一个多星期的拍摄结束，演员克鲁斯抵达[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]][[拉巴特|拉巴特]]拍摄余下的场景<ref>{{cite news|last1=Wang|first1=Yamei|title=Tom Cruise departs Vienna following Mission Impossible 5 filming|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/entertainment/2014-08/31/c_133608462.htm|accessdate=2014-08-31|publisher=xinhuanet.com|date=2014-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140831105045/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/entertainment/2014-08/31/c_133608462.htm|archive-date=2014-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=ZHAO|first1=HELEN|title=He's still got it! Tom Cruise smiles and waves to his adoring public as he arrives  in Morocco to film Mission: Impossible 5|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2738843/Tom-Cruise-smiles-waves-adoring-public-arrives-Morocco-film-Mission-Impossible-5.html|accessdate=2014-08-31|work=Daily Mail|location=UK|date=2014-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140831133046/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2738843/Tom-Cruise-smiles-waves-adoring-public-arrives-Morocco-film-Mission-Impossible-5.html|archive-date=2014-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当地的马拉喀什高速公路封闭14天（8月30日-9月12日）。摩洛哥的其他取景地包括[[阿加迪尔|阿加迪尔]]和[[拉巴特|拉巴特]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=El Barakah|first1=Tarik|title=Mission Impossible 5 Closes the Marrakech Highway for 14 Days|url=http://www.moroccoworldnews.com/2014/08/137515/mission-impossible-5-closes-the-marrakech-highway-for-14-days/|accessdate=2014-08-28|publisher=moroccoworldnews.com|date=2014-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140830102257/http://www.moroccoworldnews.com/2014/08/137515/mission-impossible-5-closes-the-marrakech-highway-for-14-days/|archive-date=2014-08-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月2日，克鲁斯被发现在[[卡萨布兰卡|卡萨布兰卡]]驾驶2015款宝马M3 Sedan轿车<ref>{{cite news|last1=Boeriu|first1=Horatiu|title=New F80 BMW M3 Featured In Mission Impossible 5|url=http://www.bmwblog.com/2014/09/03/new-f80-bmw-m3-featured-mission-impossible-5/|accessdate=2014-10-17|publisher=bmwblog.com|date=2014-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010175344/http://www.bmwblog.com/2014/09/03/new-f80-bmw-m3-featured-mission-impossible-5/|archive-date=2014-10-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Arbaoui|first1=Larbi|title=Mission Impossible 5: Cars Race through Casablanca Narrow Streets in High Speed|url=http://www.moroccoworldnews.com/2014/09/137923/mission-impossible-5-cars-drift-through-casablanca-narrow-streets-in-high-speed/|accessdate=2014-09-05|publisher=moroccoworldnews.com|date=2014-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140905070441/http://www.moroccoworldnews.com/2014/09/137923/mission-impossible-5-cars-drift-through-casablanca-narrow-streets-in-high-speed/|archive-date=2014-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Vijayenthiran|first1=Viknesh|title=2015 BMW M3 Spotted On The Set Of Mission Impossible 5: Video|url=http://www.motorauthority.com/news/1070977_2015-bmw-m3-spotted-on-the-set-of-mission-impossible-5-video|accessdate=2014-09-05|publisher=motorauthority.com|date=2014-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140905092843/http://www.motorauthority.com/news/1070977_2015-bmw-m3-spotted-on-the-set-of-mission-impossible-5-video|archive-date=2014-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月8日和9日，剧组在马拉喀什体育场进行拍摄，体育场因用来拍戏被封闭两天<ref>{{cite news|last1=El Barakah|first1=Tarik|title=After Marrakech Motorway, Mission Impossible 5 Closes down the City’s Grand Stadium|url=http://www.moroccoworldnews.com/2014/09/138105/after-marrakech-motorway-mission-impossible-5-closes-down-the-citys-grand-stadium/|accessdate=2014-09-05|publisher=moroccoworldnews.com|date=2014-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140907235931/http://www.moroccoworldnews.com/2014/09/138105/after-marrakech-motorway-mission-impossible-5-closes-down-the-citys-grand-stadium/|archive-date=2014-09-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月26日，克鲁斯在首都[[拉巴特|拉巴特]]的乌代雅城堡亲自驾驶宝马轿车做特技动作<ref>{{cite news|last1=Walker|first1=Danny|title=Mission Impossible 5: See Tom Cruise behind the wheel of stunt car on movie set|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/tv/tv-news/mission-impossible-5-see-tom-4330626|accessdate=2014-09-26|work=[[Daily_Mirror|Daily Mirror]]|location=UK|date=2014-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140929013029/http://www.mirror.co.uk/tv/tv-news/mission-impossible-5-see-tom-4330626|archive-date=2014-09-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在奥地利和摩洛哥拍摄一个多月后，剧组于9月28日移师伦敦<ref>{{cite news|last=Weitzman|first=Deborah|title=He's the man! Tom Cruise cuts a cool figure as he flashes his muscly biceps on set of new Mission Impossible 5 movie in London|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2772850/Tom-Cruise-keeps-cool-arrives-set-Mission-Impossible-5-sporting-big-headphones-flexing-biceps.html|accessdate=2014-09-30|work=Daily Mail|location=UK|date=2014-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104020627/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2772850/Tom-Cruise-keeps-cool-arrives-set-Mission-Impossible-5-sporting-big-headphones-flexing-biceps.html|archive-date=2014-11-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月7日，一辆拖车在摩洛哥的拍摄完成后，将受损的宝马M3拖走<ref>{{cite news|last1=Boeriu|first1=Horatiu|title=Lots of damaged BMW M3s spotted after Mission Impossible 5 filming|url=http://www.bmwblog.com/2014/10/07/lots-damaged-bmw-m3s-spotted-mission-impossible-5-filming/|accessdate=2014-10-17|publisher=bmwblog.com|date=2014-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141011091806/http://www.bmwblog.com/2014/10/07/lots-damaged-bmw-m3s-spotted-mission-impossible-5-filming/|archive-date=2014-10-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。10月10日，克鲁斯和他的替身演员韦德·伊斯特伍德被发现在摩纳哥拍戏<ref>{{cite news|last1=Agius|first1=Nicola|title=Taking to the Vanilla Sky: Tom Cruise and stuntman Wade Eastwood enjoy a helicopter ride while filming Mission: Impossible 5|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2788769/tom-cruise-stuntman-wade-eastwood-enjoy-helicopter-ride-filming-mission-impossible-5.html|accessdate=2014-10-17|work=Daily Mail|location=UK|date=2014-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017200024/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2788769/tom-cruise-stuntman-wade-eastwood-enjoy-helicopter-ride-filming-mission-impossible-5.html|archive-date=2014-10-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>，女主角弗格森也在场<ref>{{cite news|last1=Sedighzadeh|first1=Kazem|title=Mission Impossible 5: Tom Cruise Spotted In Monaco and Rebecca Ferguson Is Seen Performing Stunts While Shooting|url=http://masterherald.com/mission-impossible-5-tom-cruise-spotted-in-monaco-and-rebecca-ferguson-is-seen-performing-stunts-while-shooting/1666/|accessdate=2014-10-17|work=Master Herald|location=Oman|date=2014-10-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150424065803/http://masterherald.com/mission-impossible-5-tom-cruise-spotted-in-monaco-and-rebecca-ferguson-is-seen-performing-stunts-while-shooting/1666/|archivedate=2015-04-24|deadurl=no}}</ref>。伊森·亨特爬上一辆飞行中的[[空中巴士A400M|空中巴士A400M]]的动作场景在英国[[英国皇家空军|皇家空军]]威特灵基地拍摄，汤姆·克鲁斯親身上陣，其间飞机悬在5000英尺高的空中<ref>{{cite news|title=Tom Cruise scales the roof of a military aircraft for high octane Mission Impossible 5 scenes... after hanging from the plane at 5,000ft|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2819292/Tom-Cruise-scales-roof-military-aircraft-high-octane-Mission-Impossible-5-scenes-hanging-plane-5-000ft.html|accessdate=2015-02-16|work=Daily Mail|location=UK|date=2014-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220102614/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2819292/Tom-Cruise-scales-roof-military-aircraft-high-octane-Mission-Impossible-5-scenes-hanging-plane-5-000ft.html|archive-date=2014-12-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月9日，剧组在南安普顿水域拍戏，拍戏前剧组被发现抵达法雷电站<ref>{{cite news|last1=Yandell|first1=Chris|title=Megastar Tom Cruise's Mission Impossible to start filming at Fawley Power Station|url=http://www.dailyecho.co.uk/news/11588937.Shooting_for_Tom_Cruise_s_Mission_Impossible_begins_in_Southampton_water/|accessdate=2014-11-08|publisher=dailyecho.co.uk|date=2014-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129150834/http://www.dailyecho.co.uk/News/11588937.Shooting_for_Tom_Cruise_s_Mission_Impossible_begins_in_Southampton_water/|archive-date=2014-11-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年12月2日，克鲁斯在伦敦拍戏时差点被一辆双层巴士撞到。然而，这辆巴士与他擦身而过，他没有受伤<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/watch-tom-cruise-almost-get-753573 | title = Watch Tom Cruise Almost Get Hit by a Bus While Filming in London